data.description: Welcome home to this exquisite two-story luxurious townhouse that perfectly blends elegance and functionality. As you enter through the open foyer, you are greeted by the formal living room and formal dining room, creating a sophisticated atmosphere for entertaining guests. The open-concept kitchen and family room provide a seamless flow, making it easy to host gatherings and create lasting memories. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, a massive island, updated appliances, and a large walk-in pantry, ensuring all your culinary needs are met. The large family room is a cozy retreat with a wonderful gas fireplace, perfect for relaxing evenings. The main level features hardwood flooring throughout and 10 ft ceilings, creating a spacious and airy ambiance. Floor-to-ceiling windows allow an abundance of natural light to fill the space, creating a warm and inviting atmosphereadecorative crown molding throughout the townhouse adds to the elegance. Step out from the family room through French doors to a lovely private patio courtyard, adding an indoor/outdoor flow perfect for enjoying a cup of coffee or grilling out with friends. The upper level of this townhouse is equally impressive, with an extra-wide wrought iron and wood staircase leading to an upper-level landing. Here, you will find the spacious primary bedroom with a dramatic tray ceiling. The primary bathroom features a vaulted ceiling, two single marble vanities on each side of a huge soaking tub, a separate shower, and a large walk-in closet, offering a spa-like experience. Additionally, there are two secondary bedrooms with a full Jack and Jill bathroom, walk-in closets, and large windows that flood the rooms with natural light. This level also includes a convenient laundry room with a linen closet, ensuring that chores are a breeze. The townhouse offers ample storage space and a pull-down storage attic with stairs in the spacious 2-car garage. You will never be short on parking either, with a level driveway for up to 4 cars as well as family/guest parking just a stone's throw away. Located in a gated community, you can enjoy peace of mind and security. The prime location allows you to walk out the front door to restaurants and shopping, making everyday errands and entertainment a breeze. Dog-friendly community offers designated areas to relieve your furry family members. Additionally, it is just minutes away from Kennesaw State University, major highways (I-75, I-575), Town Center Mall, and shops. Only 25 minutes to downtown Atlanta and 40 minutes to Hartsfield Jackson Atlanta Airport. Don't miss the opportunity to make this lovely townhome yours and experience the epitome of luxury living. Ask about the assumable FHA loan!
